data.title: Happy heavenly birthday to Conway Twitty! Born in Mississippi on September 1st, 1933 as Harold Lloyd Jenkins, the singer showed a passion...
data.meta_description:
1,926 likes, 34 comments - countryrebel on August 31, 2023: "Happy heavenly birthday to Conway Twitty! 

Born in Mississippi on September 1st, 1933 as Harold Lloyd Jenkins, the singer showed a passion for music early in life. Twitty hosted his own radio show at the age of 12 and would go on to earn 55 #1 hits and sell 50+ million albums during his music career. 

#HappyBirthday #ConwayTwitty #ClassicCountry #HelloDarlin #CountryLegends".
